    "description": "FIITJEE Consulting Pvt Ltd, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Subject Matter Expert for our Chennai operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout FIITJEE Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nFIITJEE Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in Educational Technology\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with FIITJEE Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
